headline: EXPE Q4 Earnings Beat on Strong B2B and Advertising Growth
summary: Expedia Group's Q4 earnings beat estimates as B2B bookings jump 24% and advertising surges, lifting revenues 11% year over year.

headline: 1 Volatile Stock on Our Buy List and 2 Facing Headwinds
summary: Volatility cuts both ways - while it creates opportunities, it also increases risk, making sharp declines just as likely as big gains. This unpredictability can shake out even the most experienced investors.
